Here are the public test cases for feature12_named_crs:
{
  "description": "A named coordinate reference system identifies a CRS by name. It exposes a type marker indicating a named system and carries the name under a dedicated property key. When attached to a GeoJSON object it serializes as a nested object containing that property and the named-system type marker. Construction rejects a null name as a missing required argument and an empty name as invalid. Two named systems with the same name compare equal and share a hash code; different names compare unequal with differing hash codes.",
  "cases": [
    {
      "input": {
        "op": "make_crs",
        "crs": {
          "kind": "named",
          "name": "EPSG:31370"
        }
      },
      "expected_output": "type=name\nprop.name=EPSG:31370\n"
    },
    {
      "input": {
        "op": "serialize",
        "object": {
          "kind": "feature_collection",
          "features": [],
          "crs": {
            "kind": "named",
            "name": "EPSG:31370"
          }
        },
        "formatting": "none"
      },
      "expected_output": "{\"type\":\"FeatureCollection\",\"features\":[],\"crs\":{\"properties\":{\"name\":\"EPSG:31370\"},\"type\":\"name\"}}\n"
    }
  ]
}

Here are the public test cases for feature13_linked_crs:
{
  "description": "A linked coordinate reference system references a CRS by dereferenceable URI, optionally with a link type. It exposes a type marker indicating a linked system and carries the href, and the optional type, under dedicated property keys. When attached to a GeoJSON object it serializes as a nested object and is read back from that same shape. Construction rejects a null href as a missing required argument, an empty href as invalid, and an href that is not a dereferenceable URI as invalid; a relative reference is accepted. Two linked systems with the same href compare equal and share a hash code; different hrefs compare unequal.",
  "cases": [
    {
      "input": {
        "op": "make_crs",
        "crs": {
          "kind": "linked",
          "href": "http://localhost"
        }
      },
      "expected_output": "type=link\nprop.href=http://localhost\n"
    },
    {
      "input": {
        "op": "make_crs",
        "crs": {
          "kind": "linked",
          "href": "http://localhost",
          "type": "ogcwkt"
        }
      },
      "expected_output": "type=link\nprop.href=http://localhost\nprop.type=ogcwkt\n"
    },
    {
      "input": {
        "op": "make_crs",
        "crs": {
          "kind": "linked",
          "href": "http://not-a-valid-<>-url"
        }
      },
      "expected_output": "error=argument_invalid\nparam=href\nreason=must_be_dereferenceable_uri\n"
    }
  ]
}

